{
  "stem": "8423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And spending that kind of time in the cattle cars, they were in pretty bad shape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they were helping people down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually, finally, somebody had to help me down, because I didn't jump.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this man in this blue and white striped uniform came over to me, totally emaciated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, he looked like an absolute living skeleton.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He has a little round cap from the same cloth as his uniform was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember on his shaved head, it was just riding back and forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said to me, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, 14.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I really wasn't 14 yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had my 14th birthday in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're not 14.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're 16, 16.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He spoke in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, you're 16.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, no, my sister over there, she is 16.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he turned to her, and he said, you're 17.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then he handed me down to my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course they put us quickly into lines of five.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they started marching us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was all kinds of screaming and chaos, because they were separating the families.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very-- extremely rapidly, extremely rapidly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because so much was happening that, you know, even that made it all sound-- we were being rushed, rushed, rushed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS] Schnell, schnell, schnell is all we heard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we saw German soldiers on horses, horseback, riding between us, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were trying to beat us into the line-- five abreast, five abreast, men to the right, women to the left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as they were being separated-- sons, mothers, fathers, brothers, you know, husbands, wives-- as they were being pulled apart, there was such crying and carrying on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just absolutely unbelievable to describe.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
